title: Status Duration.
text:
WhatsApp team, 
For the most part, the app has been effective in keeping touch with friends and family, but there is always room for improvement.
Currently, users can only pin statuses for 24 hours, which can be limiting for those who want to share important updates that may need to stay up for longer periods of time. I think it would be helpful if users are allowed to choose how long they prefer a single or multiple shared status to stay pinned on duration, whether that's 24 hours, 48 hours, or even longer. 
Overall, extending the duration for pinned statuses on WhatsApp would enhance the user experience and provide more customization options for individuals to curate their profiles and share important information with their contacts. Hope this is deliberated on and implemented asap.ğŸ™‚
Thanks.
